{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/posts/CSS/css_align/","result":{"data":{"logo":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","width":400,"height":128,"src":"/static/2b5eaa0de166a8b5faebad4955c2200c/3891b/ghost-logo.png","srcSet":"/static/2b5eaa0de166a8b5faebad4955c2200c/3891b/ghost-logo.png 1x"}}},"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"intro\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#intro\" aria-label=\"intro permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Intro</h1>\n<p>CSS에는 속성을 적을 때 순서가 상관이 없기 때문에 마음대로 편하게 적을 수 있다. (속성이 겹치는 경우는 제외)\n하지만 속성의 순서를 신경을 안 쓴 채 작성된 CSS문서는 다른사람이 볼 때 특정 속성을 찾으려 할 때 불편하다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"css-선언-규칙\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#css-%EC%84%A0%EC%96%B8-%EA%B7%9C%EC%B9%99\" aria-label=\"css 선언 규칙 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CSS 선언 규칙</h1>\n<p>협업을 할 때 서로서로 CSS를 마음대로 작성해서 파일을 열어 특정속성을 수정할 때 눈이 빠지게 찾는 걸 방지하기 위해 CSS선언하는 것에 대해 규칙을 세우는것이 필요하다.</p>\n<p>Mozilla, 네이버, 다음에서는 다음과 같이 선언순서를 제안하고 있다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"mozilla-재단\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#mozilla-%EC%9E%AC%EB%8B%A8\" aria-label=\"mozilla 재단 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Mozilla 재단</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>display</li>\n<li>list-style</li>\n<li>position</li>\n<li>float</li>\n<li>clear</li>\n<li>width / height</li>\n<li>padding / margin</li>\n<li>border / background</li>\n<li>color / font</li>\n<li>text-decoration</li>\n<li>text-align / vertical-align</li>\n<li>white-space</li>\n<li>other text</li>\n<li>content</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"naver\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#naver\" aria-label=\"naver permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>NAVER</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>display(표시)</li>\n<li>overflow(넘침)</li>\n<li>float(흐름)</li>\n<li>position(위치)</li>\n<li>width/height(크기)</li>\n<li>padding/margin(간격)</li>\n<li>border(테두리)</li>\n<li>background(배경)</li>\n<li>color/font(글꼴)</li>\n<li>animation</li>\n<li>기타</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"daum\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#daum\" aria-label=\"daum permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>DAUM</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>display</li>\n<li>overflow</li>\n<li>float</li>\n<li>position</li>\n<li>z-index</li>\n<li>width &#x26; height</li>\n<li>margin &#x26; padding</li>\n<li>border</li>\n<li>font</li>\n<li>background</li>\n<li>기타</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"선택은-자유\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%84%A0%ED%83%9D%EC%9D%80-%EC%9E%90%EC%9C%A0\" aria-label=\"선택은 자유 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>선택은 자유</h2>\n<p>CSS를 작성하는데에는 맞다 틀리다가 없다. 이 위의 규칙을 따라도 돼고 자신만의 규칙을 만들어서 써도됀다. 다만, 다른 이가 봣을때 이해하기 쉽게 작성하자.</p>\n<h2 id=\"learn-more\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#learn-more\" aria-label=\"learn more permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.4